  Z['docs.section1.p']='Claude Code 启动时按以下优先级加载指令文件：'; E['docs.section1.p']='Claude Code loads instruction files in this priority order on startup:';
  Z['docs.section1.li1']='<code>~/.claude/CLAUDE.md</code> — 全局个人指令，所有项目生效'; E['docs.section1.li1']='<code>~/.claude/CLAUDE.md</code> — Global personal instructions, applies to all projects';
