  Z['localMd.template.footer']='## 说明\n以上偏好会在每次 Claude Code 会话中加载（在 CLAUDE.md 之后加载），仅对当前项目生效。\n如需在所有项目中生效，请将偏好移至 ~/.claude/CLAUDE.md。'; E['localMd.template.footer']='## Notes\nThese preferences are loaded in every Claude Code session (after CLAUDE.md), for the current project only.\nTo apply globally, move them to ~/.claude/CLAUDE.md.';

